{"tid":1355009,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"再有拆墳行動前 請義士準備加密貨幣收款地址","createTime":"2019-07-23T08:49:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T08:49:48.000Z","uid":47194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8656a2dcdf82109292f35b736687be5983f3e46b","tid":1355009,"uid":47194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:49:48.000Z","msg":"何君妖家墳被滑倒，有相有中指，成件事美中不足，就係差個加密貨幣收款地址/QRCode，下次義士做類似行動記得帶埋去，有3個方法：<br />\n<br />\n1. 影相，QRCode或收款地址，圖要夠高清，紙質不要太厚，方便判斷是否改圖，發佈前移除EXIF<br />\n2. 拍幾秒短片揚一揚張紙<br />\n3. 噴上收款地址、太長的話可以用短網址服務(<a href=\"https://bitly.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbitly.com&d=DQhhZyJ%2BQntsVA7gHYVTWHPcKSbPy461JM9tWmz6mNY%3D&h=9ff65f10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bitly.com</a>)縮短，用 &quot;http://{btc addr}.btc&quot; 格式輸入，大家會明。<br />\n<br />\n提現用 <a href=\"https://localbitcoins.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flocalbitcoins.com&d=DQhhZyJ%2BQntsVA7gHYVTWHPcKSbPy461JM9tWmz6mNY%3D&h=3b4a3a10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://localbitcoins.com</a>。<br />\n<br />\n最好玩嘅係公眾係可以睇倒有幾多課金。香港人為加密貨幣創造偉大用途，繼委內瑞拉後成為第二個區塊鏈救國案例，震憾國際。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ua4byEz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fua4byEz.jpg&h=54492deb&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}